RustyTalon retains substantial portions of IronClaw's architecture, particularly:
- WASM sandbox implementation (src/tools/wasm/)
- Safety/security layers (src/safety/)
- Database abstraction (src/db/)
- Workspace/memory system
- Signal channel integration

The following were significantly modified or replaced:
- LLM provider system: Removed NEAR AI dependency, added multi-provider support
  (Anthropic, OpenAI, Ollama, OpenAI-compatible)
- Build scripts and deployment configuration
- Docker containerization
- API routing and smart provider selection

